  <brief_title>Calf Muscle Strength and Standing Efficiency in Children With Spastic Diplegia</brief_title>
  <official_title>CALF MUSCLE STRENGTH AND STANDING EFFICIENCY IN CHILDREN WITH SPASTIC DIPLEGIA: A RANDOMIZED CONTROLLED TRIAL</official_title>
